Stakes Doubled argues that Daley spearheaded an attempt to replace Biden despite their &quot;close personal relationship&quot; but ultimately backed out when their data showed that adding Clinton to the electoral list would not &quot;significantly improve Obama&#39;s chances. &quot;.
